### column
column-count:  
column-width:  
column-gap:  
官方onlie demo： https://jsfiddle.net/api/mdn/  
```
.grid_container {
  column-width: 250px;
  column-gap: 20px;
}

.grid_card {
  break-inside: avoid;
  page-break-inside: avoid;
  background-color: rgb(207, 232, 220);
  border: 2px solid rgb(79, 185, 227);
  padding: 10px;
  margin: 0 0 1em 0;
}
```


